# SPA runtime configuration. Vite exposes any variable prefixed with VITE_ to
# the client bundle. Copy to `.env` (or `.env.local`) for local development.
#
# Base URL the SPA hits for API calls. Leave unset for the default self-hosted
# setup where the SPA and API share an origin behind a reverse proxy or the
# Vite dev proxy. Set to an absolute URL to point the SPA at a remote API
# (e.g. `https://api.example.com/v1`).
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api/v1
